rows.label: tlk4140004301_msg0001
rows.name:
Thanks a lot for picking me! I can tell
you're a great bunch.

rows.label: tlk4140004301_msg0002
rows.name:
The big man's a tough act to follow,
but I see you've already earned their
trust.

rows.label: tlk4140004301_msg0003
rows.name:
Well then, I'll do my very best to live
up to your expectations!
